The paper discusses the development of an AI tool for acquiring knowledge in software engineering, specifically in understanding static code warnings. This falls under the sub-category of software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of static code analysis, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the use of an expert system for acquiring knowledge can also be related to systems and control (cs.SY).
